{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means this side of the Carpathians, not [NON-ENGLISH], the other side, which faced Poland at that time, which was also Ukrainian territory.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we have-- we have been living there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a huge, big room where the whole family lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, they usually had two or three children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were living at one part of room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were the goats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The goats were in the same room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only difference is they were in one side of the room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were living in another side room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we as forced laborers, we were living on top of the-- of-- of the wire-- wire top of the-- where the goats were fenced in and had the wire top.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And if you would ask me today if the goat smelled or we smelled, I couldn't tell the difference because the goats-- the minute we have come home, we were so dead tired that we went to sleep immediately.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I have to tell you about these trees-- tree trunks, which were cleaned of the branches.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had the one man in the front, the other one in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if you're lucky, then they put in another two men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It depends how heavy the tree trunks were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we started to carry those tree trunks in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in the afternoon, we reached the top where the trees were supposed to be needed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we moved from here-- from-- from this-- from [NON-ENGISH] to [NON-ENGLISH], then it changed a little bit, the situation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were also living at the different private homes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we had a private room with other goats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We missed the goats because they were warm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And with other goats, the room was cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We have--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
